Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:11:17.02,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)}Note: there's really bad audio lag for the first entire half of this stream.\NNot much I can do about it, sorry :/
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:58.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk "This story continues with hope" Edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:04.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Was that alright? Sorry, I bumped the mic a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Kon-more!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This is Mayu Yoshioka, voice of Haruka Kiritani from MMJ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:17.02,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,In this edition of ProSeka Aftertalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:24.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we'll look back at this event while covering messages you, the fans, have sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:28.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This time, we'll be covering the "This story continues with hope" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:34.57,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Have you been enjoying the event and the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,What do you all think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:40.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I've personally been really looking forward this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:46.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Today, especially, since I get to hear everyone's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:52.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We've gathered your comments for this Aftertalk sent through email as well as the submissions channel on the Discord .
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:55.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you to everyone who mailed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:58.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We'd like to go over some of them in our program today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:03.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We got so many, but unfortunately due to time we're only going to be able to cover a few,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.43,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but we do appreciate each and every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.33,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Also, if you have any thoughts on today's program,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,please post them on X with #ProSekaAftertalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We'll also be watching the YouTube chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Please keep all the messages coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'll also check the Aftertalk hashtag after the program today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:25.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,so please make sure to post there as well. We'd appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:31.59,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright then, I'll be sure to keep up with the YouTube chat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:33.48,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but we've got a lot to get through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I also came with a lot to talk about, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,〣 ( ºΔº ) 〣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:42.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I brought my notebook for today, but I forgot it in the green room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.83,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll ask one of the makeup artists to help me get it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:53.55,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll start off by talking about the "This story continues with hope" event story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:58.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,How did you feel about the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:04.54,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Let's revisit the highlights of this story together while going over some of the messages you’ve sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:10.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,First up, from "Mirin"-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:13.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message, Mirin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Yoshioka-san, 'kon-more'". Kon-more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.77,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I loved your firm yet clear voice."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:20.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:27.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I feel like this event showed a lot more of the deliberation than usual."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:32.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This time, MMJ were working together with the other idol groups like Cheer Day towards the same goal."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.45,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"And by working together—"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mindblown emoji{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:40.88,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They brought it over for me. We'll go over this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Sorry for interrupting your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:48.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This time, MMJ were working together with the other idol groups like Cheer Day towards the same goal."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:54.33,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Being able to see everyone talking things through, exchanging ideas, and going back and forth on different approaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:58.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"and through it all, Haruka-chan taking charge to get things done was really cool to see."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:01.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This was another great chance to see Haruka taking the initiative."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:05.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"It was fun to see her work together with all the other idols."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:10.01,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Do your best at the LumiGra finals, MMJ!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.50,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the abbreviation, "LumiGra".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Shortened from "Lumina Grand Prix."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:21.27,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think that's the first time I've seened it shortened like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Have I seen that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Either way, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.43,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Appreciate you writing in, Mirin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:36.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,, That's right, we are at a really important point in the story. This is the stage right before the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:40.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This is the stage where we finally get to see everyone's votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:46.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I know everyone had big expectations for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.76,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, I did see lots of people saying "oh boy here it comes..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I feel like they're in great shape to tackle whatever comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I want Haruka as my boss."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.73,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"First time seeing 'LumiGra—'" oh, interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.27,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Looks like that's how some are saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually yeah, that does sound like what people might call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,LumiGra sounds right. Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:29.57,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, we have one more message to go over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:34.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,From "Yukki"-san, thank you. That's "Yukki" in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Kon-more, Yoshioka-san!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Kon-more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:41.59,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I felt like this story represented a culmination of MMJ's recent efforts."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:44.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Seeing the formerly competing idol groups join forces,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"not just to impress the viewers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:52.55,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"but prioritizing bringing hope to their audience, was really moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:58.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"On top of that, we saw Haruka confronting some of her past trauma as a way of getting through their challenges."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I thought that was extremely cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:04.37,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"And at the end, they were able to get 2nd overall in qualifiers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"and I was yet again moved."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:09.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Yoshioka-san, I'm looking forward to all the ways you'll continue to portray Haruka-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely. I so relieved they managed to get 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:19.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But waiting for that announcement was really nerve-wracking, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hearing everyone else get announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:27.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, isn't them announcing the number of votes before the group super realistic too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:32.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Isn't it kind of interesting how everyone gets two votes for this event?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:37.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,You just have to choose just one, you can go "these guys" and "these guys".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:41.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That's a very forgiving system, and seeing the number of comments too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:49.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it really allowed them to see exactly how much attention they were actually getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Makes for a pretty interesting event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:17:03.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,In real life, you don't really see too many of these kind of nation-wide idol competitons,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:09.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I found myself thinking "what would this look like if it happened in real life?" a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:14.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I voted for MMJ and ReLight! (jk)"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:17.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, who would I vote for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:23.39,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean, there were a few units mentioned that didn't directly show up in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:29.59,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I liked wondering what those groups might have been like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:34.02,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think someone mentioned, you can't use both your votes on the same unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Think it was mentioned somewhere in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:43.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! "The moment 4th place was announced, someone knew they were going home."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:48.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hearing that not everyone in their group was making it through must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I get that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:54.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That other unit "Aimu" did end up passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,, I wonder what they're like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Getting 2nd is huge win for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:14.33,Haruka,,0,0,0,,In the first episode, before the event, Haruka talked about how MMJ should expect a certain position based on the current online rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:20.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I totally get that, trying to get a feel out how the final rankings might end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:24.06,Haruka,,0,0,0,,MMJ were definitely checking out all the rankings and predictions on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:33.24,Haruka,,0,0,0,,All of that might have an influence on their production direction after this event
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:37.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Proactively seeking out all that information online, and then deciding on a strategy from there;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:41.06,Haruka,,0,0,0,,isn't that really mature of them? Especially since they're high schoolers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:45.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,How the heck can high schoolers be that smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:49.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for your message, Yukki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:53.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We only got to read these 3 messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:58.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I have so much I want to talk about too, so I'm going to take over a bit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The Lumina Grand Prix was,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:12.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,for all you ProSeka users, it must definitely feel like it's been going on for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:14.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After all, the story is shown just bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:19.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I totally get people saying "When are we gonna get to the finals?" or "I wanna see what happens next!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:24.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But actually, I kind of want to just stay right here in this little gap right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:27.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,after all the hard work in the qualifiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:31.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,right between passing the qualifiers and before the finals start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Even I was really nervous about the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So when I heard this would be a Haruka focus event, I was like "ahhhhh"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:42.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm covering {\i1}this{\i0} part of the story as a Haruka focus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And especially for Haruka,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we'll go more in depth later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:52.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but it's very obvious that there's a big wall between Haruka and Hiiragi-san, ReLight's producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Something Haruka can't really ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:59.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And the fact that she has to come face to face with home once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Last time she...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:05.69,Haruka,,0,0,0,,fought with him? Not quite "fought", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:10.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Last time she confronted him face to face,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:17.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it almost felt like this standoff between grown-ups in the corporate world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:21.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After which, Haruka had this really down look,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,like "I don't know how we're going to get through this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:29.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I think she grew from that. And so when she went to face Hiiragi-san again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:34.42,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what exactly the confrontation might look like this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:40.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But considering they're now working with ReLight in the stage right before finals,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:46.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad she got such reassuring advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:51.24,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That feeling of security and strength from know that Hiiragi-san has their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Knowing he's this big, influential figure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:57.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She must feel so relieved knowing "ah, Hiiragi-san has our backs."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,You could feel that coming from each and every word that he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:06.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think Haruka does truly have respect and admiration for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:11.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but at the same time, she knows that someday, she'll have to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:17.48,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That acknowledgement, I feel, was more or less the focus of Episode 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:23.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,He's scary, that Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:29.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's like, the more you rely on him, the more he feels like he's going to be a threat later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:43.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So it makes me really wonder, what kind of team was ASRUN back when Hiiragi-san and Haruka were working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:47.46,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So Haruka's main battle was with Hiiragi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:51.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but that's wrapped in the wider context of preparing for the event for the cram school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:58.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And all the other teams going to their own various locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:03.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Arisawa-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:07.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,ideas? As a former idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:11.27,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hearing her perspective on "this is what I wish I could have done for them".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:15.48,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Even if she's retired, she sees the idols of today and thinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:20.60,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I want ensure this generation has that strength to deliver hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:26.18,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ensuring the idols of this world have that... "allure?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:28.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think that's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:33.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean come on, having that kind of expectation from this legendary idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:36.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,you guys sure have your work cut out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:39.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"The story got me really fired up."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:50.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah that one was good—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:53.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Kiritani really is dangerous, getting me fired up like that." 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:55.83,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I really like that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:59.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For event recordings, we usually only get to see the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:07.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We don't usually record together, so I only get to see the full conversations in-game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:13.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But even just looking at the script, I knew that scene with Hiiragi-san and Arisawa-san was going to be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:16.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:19.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,that was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:22.57,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was actually going through the story mostly to get to that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:25.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, I did want to see the rest of MMJ's scenes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:29.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But that scene was specifically one I wanted to burn into my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:35.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah. Looks like the audio's a bit out of sync so we're going to pause the stream momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:38.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Please standby while we fix the issue.
Comment: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:33.69,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--We're back--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.69,0:24:40.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright then, we've been talking a lot about Chapter 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.16,0:24:43.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but let's talk about what happens in the other chapters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.93,0:24:46.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like the excursion live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:52.97,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Two whole weeks for that— if you think about the fact that the whole Lumina Grand Prix leading up to this was less than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.97,0:24:55.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,, isn't that pretty crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.61,0:25:00.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They've all had to shuffle teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.63,0:25:03.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and then learn each others' songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.19,0:25:07.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and if you think about the fact that they could do that in just a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.30,0:25:11.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,you can tell everyone's gotta have a really young memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.17,0:25:16.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how fast these practice parts go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.47,0:25:20.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Especially with how fast they must have to learn new songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.65,0:25:26.76,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Minori's mentioned that she's good at imitating choreo,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.76,0:25:32.31,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but for other members who aren't so good at that having to learn so quickly—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.31,0:25:35.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,not just the choreo, but the singing parts, the rest of the formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.92,0:25:39.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and{\i0} bringing their own originality while keeping respect for the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.81,0:25:42.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Isn't that way too much to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.09,0:25:43.77,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Aren't they just so talented?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.77,0:25:45.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I need to start learning from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:50.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They're super impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.13,0:25:55.88,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's one thing I saw that I couldn't stop laughing at.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.92,0:26:07.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The comments. For all the recent MMJ events, you sometimes see the stream viewers' comments pop up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:10.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you all aren't the ones writing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.63,0:26:14.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually I think I've seen them before,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.08,0:26:17.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I feel like there's actually a writer specifically for those comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.72,0:26:21.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"They're always really accurate."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.64,0:26:25.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,People are probably like "wait, did they steal that from my tweet?"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.84,0:26:32.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"You got me." Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.63,0:26:35.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, are they just taking those comments from online,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.99,0:26:39.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,or are they recruiting the actual commenters?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.03,0:26:41.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I always find it super funny to think about how accurate they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.99,0:26:48.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hmm, but I think that's just one part of how realistic these stories have been feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.96,0:26:55.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,In each story, I always like thinking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.64,0:26:59.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"which comments are the ones I'm most likely to have said?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.81,0:27:09.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, there are also times where those comments are actually spoken in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.72,0:27:13.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Any time the fans themselves show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.38,0:27:18.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, for some of the lines from MMJ fans or Cheerful＊Days fans, you'd think;
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.68,0:27:21.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Ahh, I'd definitely say something like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.11,0:27:30.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, and you know, I'm glad we don't hear this as much nowadays,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.80,0:27:33.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we don't see it as much, but earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.80,0:27:36.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,there were lots of comments like "MMJ? Who?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.73,0:27:40.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Especially for Minori...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.07,0:27:44.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,people saying things like "I've been following the other members, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.28,0:27:49.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,there were... there were some pretty tough comments out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.34,0:27:53.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But if you compare it to now, don't you think they've come so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.16,0:27:56.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,All the comments are like "Go MMJ!"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.04,0:27:57.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.99,0:28:06.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"The comments are so much nicer now."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.65,0:28:09.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not only nicer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.05,0:28:15.44,Haruka,,0,0,0,,they must be so glad that they're really well known now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:18.44,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like they've even been featured on TV now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.24,0:28:24.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Comments do have real power, don't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.56,0:28:31.59,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"It's their hard work". 100%, it's MMJ hard work paying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.91,0:28:41.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Everyone's feels super welcomed by the comments now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.08,0:28:43.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They're not worried reading them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.01,0:28:49.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.15,0:28:53.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I feel like if MMJ was to solo stream,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.09,0:28:57.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,the comment section would have a pretty different vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.64,0:29:01.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, there were fans who have been with them all the way since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.75,0:29:04.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and I feel that part wouldn't change,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.04,0:29:06.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I bet there'd be lots of comments like "Hey, I'm new here!" Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.61,0:29:10.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I just came from learning about MMJ at the Lumina Grand Prix!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.08,0:29:12.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.64,0:29:16.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I'm originally a Cheerful＊Days fan, but got interested in MMJ, so I joined their stream!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.13,0:29:18.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Something like that hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.97,0:29:24.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hahaha "Newbies! Welcome!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:30.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Everyone'd be like "Welcome!" "Welcome!" Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.13,0:29:34.25,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Oh, you're a first-timer?" Yeah I could see people saying that haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.17,0:29:43.83,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Welcome all first-timers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.83,0:29:46.71,Haruka,,0,0,0,,All the veterans might say that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.71,0:29:51.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. "I came from watching the LumiGra."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.29,0:29:55.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Wait, what if LumiGra actually becomes term official staff use?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.29,0:29:57.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. It's just me calling it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.59,0:30:00.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.99,0:30:05.06,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That was a bit of a recap on the story as a whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.06,0:30:06.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.79,0:30:08.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,let's set aside the Chapter 8 discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.63,0:30:11.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,There's actually a specific scene I wanted to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.38,0:30:14.45,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I've chosen a scene I wanted to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.45,0:30:16.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,As you might expect, it's from Chapter 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.99,0:30:18.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:23.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was thinking Chapter 8 too,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.29,0:30:25.25,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I would start crying if we watched that.
Comment: 0,0:30:25.25,0:30:28.25,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--END PRE-STORY TALK --
Comment: 0,0:38:18.13,0:38:18.13,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--BEGIN POST STORY TALK--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.13,0:38:23.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, that was Chapter 6 of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.38,0:38:31.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mentioned it a little before we watched, but that conversation between Haruka and Hiiragi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.35,0:38:38.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I thought the bravery Haruka showed to directly confront him one-on-one was absolutely incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.23,0:38:44.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Knowing that they already faced off during Haruka’s previous focus event, but even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.72,0:38:47.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,still going to meet him again like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.32,0:38:50.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it shows that she has a very different mindset now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.26,0:38:53.48,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I thought that was really cool of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.48,0:38:58.24,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For that confrontation scene, we actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.24,0:38:59.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we actually did two takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.84,0:39:01.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think they ended up using the second take.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.82,0:39:04.31,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After going through the first take—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.31,0:39:08.76,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean, for Haruka to go up to Hiiragi-san, this really distinguished producer,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.76,0:39:13.59,Haruka,,0,0,0,,she would definitely have {\i1}some {\i0}nerves. Maybe feeling like "I don't know what to do next".
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.59,0:39:19.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So I talked with more of a wavering, unsure tone, like she was kind of just casually going to ask for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.00,0:39:21.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But they said, "no, this is—"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.70,0:39:25.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Let Haruka fight for this."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.47,0:39:26.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"With Hiiragi-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.70,0:39:30.89,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, "To get that advice out of him, you need to go in there and {\i1}hunt{\i0} for it."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.89,0:39:33.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But that means you really need to approach him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.20,0:39:40.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Fight him on this; say that we need to cooperate in order ensure we pass."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.15,0:39:41.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I got that direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.13,0:39:44.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and I was like "wow, sounds fun, let's try it."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.67,0:39:47.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And so that's how the second take turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.84,0:39:59.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, I feel that one focal point point of this story is Haruka taking these small steps forward on her journey as a producer herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.47,0:40:05.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I really hope that came through clearly in this scene with Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.72,0:40:07.83,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.83,0:40:10.73,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The sound producers and directors have all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.73,0:40:14.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,little by little building this character of Haruka alongside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.28,0:40:20.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So hearing them say more things like, "Maybe it's time for Haruka to show a bit of her strength here," makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.12,0:40:26.44,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That particularly comes through in this Chapter 6, so I really wanted to watch it with everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.44,0:40:28.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.35,0:40:30.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.86,0:40:33.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my earring fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.86,0:40:40.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.35,0:40:44.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Right, so we'll leave the Chapter 6 discussion at that, and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.87,0:40:46.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,time for the card art, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.92,0:40:52.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.15,0:40:54.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We're gonna talk about Chapter 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.52,0:40:56.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Chapter 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.32,0:40:58.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.52,0:41:02.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,first and foremost, congrats on passing, MMJ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.92,0:41:04.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Big congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.68,0:41:09.06,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I thought that just making finals would be great,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.06,0:41:12.06,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but to get second place? Aren't they so amazing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.46,0:41:16.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So 1st place was Cheerful＊Days,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.05,0:41:17.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and MMJ got 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.29,0:41:24.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After 3rd and 4th were announced and there were only 2 teams left, hearing Haruka not wanting to give up—
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.93,0:41:28.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.00,0:41:29.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She was so cool in that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.86,0:41:33.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Even as the other members were losing hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.29,0:41:35.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,she was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.32,0:41:39.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,ah, I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.16,0:41:40.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But yeah, that was just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.65,0:41:42.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Seeing her say "We can't give up" like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.17,0:41:46.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And then her being the first to go up and say "Thank you" as their representative....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.16,0:41:50.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That "Thank you" honestly made me burst into tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.34,0:41:52.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is all Haruka. I’m just speaking as her,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.78,0:41:55.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but man, everything about this scene just makes me just so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.75,0:41:57.77,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.77,0:42:02.50,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For that "Thank you"... let's see,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.50,0:42:05.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think we ended up doing two takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.38,0:42:09.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For the first one, I felt like I had to stay composed and speak very straightforwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.61,0:42:12.42,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But they said, "Maybe it's okay let a little more emotion out."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.42,0:42:14.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This is a big moment in the story after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.14,0:42:15.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I thought "You're so right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.75,0:42:19.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So I went for it again, and it came out amazingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.08,0:42:22.46,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was like "I'm crying again even the second time around?"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.46,0:42:25.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It really was a "thank you" from the bottom of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.99,0:42:29.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, Hikarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.74,0:42:32.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She got a respectable 5th place,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.17,0:42:35.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but only the top 4 moved on from the qualifiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.04,0:42:40.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,so unfortunately that means this is the end of Hikarin's dream, at least for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.96,0:42:45.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But she said she believes that everyone will continue to shine their best in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.85,0:42:50.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think Hikarin's unique style really helped everyone in this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.51,0:42:52.43,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Especially Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.43,0:42:57.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Seeing her leave even after building that bond with everyone is definitely sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.51,0:43:01.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but seeing everyone's hopes and dreams come together,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.13,0:43:08.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,that really made this stand out as a "team" effort for this final qualifier round.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.60,0:43:18.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Also, on a personal note, I was so happy when Hikarin’s character visual was finally added!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.97,0:43:21.69,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I've always been super curious about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.69,0:43:24.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I had an idea just based on her voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.20,0:43:26.89,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but finally seeing her, she's just super cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.89,0:43:29.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,There's just so much going on in her design.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.17,0:43:34.02,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I really just wanted to learn more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.02,0:43:36.57,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I hope they get to perform together again one day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.57,0:43:40.43,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I’m also curious about what kind of songs Hikarin actually sings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.26,0:43:43.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.96,0:43:48.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So, we'll move on to card art discussion in a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.23,0:43:51.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and in Airi's? Yeah, in Airi's card, Hikarin shows up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.23,0:43:58.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it. When you build up a "persona" too much, it gets really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.98,0:44:02.39,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Keeping up a persona is definitely a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.39,0:44:07.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She'll definitely get over it one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.19,0:44:12.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But it's because she overcame that struggle that we can see Hikarin as she is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.10,0:44:13.59,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm really rooting for her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.59,0:44:18.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And as for what lies ahead in the finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.08,0:44:21.94,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it's finally coming. Remember, this has all just been the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.94,0:44:25.24,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's only gonna get tougher from here. Just four teams left standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.24,0:44:30.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm excited to see exactly what's in store for them going forward.
Comment: 0,0:44:31.93,0:44:37.67,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--BEGIN CARD TALK--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.93,0:44:34.54,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that, let's move on to the event cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.02,0:44:39.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, then, to start us off...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.21,0:44:44.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Haruka-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.80,0:44:48.29,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.29,0:44:51.29,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}This was super cool, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.29,0:44:54.49,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}When her banner event was announced,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.49,0:44:57.24,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I felt like I needed to fix my posture\Nand stand up straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.24,0:45:02.47,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I remember grinning to myself, like "nah, she'd win."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.47,0:45:03.67,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hiiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.67,0:45:04.75,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I was like "Hiii!"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.75,0:45:06.22,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Thank you for the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.22,0:45:06.87,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Yeah, guys, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.87,0:45:07.77,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.46,0:45:17.00,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I mean come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.00,0:45:21.03,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Oh, you can't see what I'm pointing at.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.03,0:45:24.19,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These gloves. They're the kind that aren't— full?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.19,0:45:26.37,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}They don't come down all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.37,0:45:27.89,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}What do you call those?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.89,0:45:29.13,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I mean, these were like—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.13,0:45:31.96,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These look amazing on our Haruka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.96,0:45:34.55,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.55,0:45:38.20,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Gotta remember to talk about the whole costume\Nafter these little detailed parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.20,0:45:41.20,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And those sparkles are also so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.13,0:45:47.45,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Gotta keep moving on. Else we'll be here all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.45,0:45:48.57,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.57,0:45:51.38,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Yeah, this is the one I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.38,0:45:53.65,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hikarin and Airi in the cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.65,0:45:56.16,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These two were also really cute~
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.16,0:45:58.69,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Kind of looks like they're part of a talk show.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.69,0:46:02.00,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Definitely looks like they're\Nready to liven the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.00,0:46:08.04,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,810)}So cute. Actually, when I first saw her character sprite, Hikarin was a bit shorter than I was expecting,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.04,0:46:09.24,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}but I think that makes her cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.56,0:46:15.88,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Airi's also really good here, isn't she? And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.88,0:46:18.52,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So pretty here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.52,0:46:20.47,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.47,0:46:22.60,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Yeah, try rotating her straight up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.60,0:46:24.63,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Think it looks really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.74,0:46:31.32,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Lighting is so pretty, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.32,0:46:34.15,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And the illumination from the back, like
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.15,0:46:37.32,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(650,750)}Kasaaa{\i0}. So good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.43,0:46:39.96,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.96,0:46:41.50,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Right, gotta keep looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.50,0:46:44.50,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Otherwise you'll only get a view of my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.09,0:46:48.77,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah, Len-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.68,0:46:53.38,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}This was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.33,0:46:57.77,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Oh look, there’s a little penguin on her notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.77,0:46:58.95,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.95,0:47:01.06,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}We know Haruka loves her penguins.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.06,0:47:02.77,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}She even has one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.58,0:47:09.03,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Wait a sec, I think she even has a penguin thing\N on her pencil case.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.03,0:47:12.25,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Actually, I think Len's sprite has...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.25,0:47:14.95,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}his old costume? Can you call it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.95,0:47:17.19,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}The one he started with.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.19,0:47:21.48,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}But seeing his new outfit in a card art like this is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.61,0:47:24.74,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And here's cool Len.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.27,0:47:30.10,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Beautiful. Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.10,0:47:33.21,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}It's too much, I can't even look at him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.21,0:47:34.72,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.72,0:47:36.33,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.33,0:47:38.38,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah this was also so goodー
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.38,0:47:41.88,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}wait a sec, is this really only a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.88,0:47:43.32,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Just a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.32,0:47:47.50,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah, so cute, so pretty, just as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.50,0:47:50.65,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}She's so dazzling. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.65,0:47:54.43,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And the trained. Are you sure this is a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.25,0:47:57.49,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Is this really a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.49,0:47:59.28,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I don't even know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.28,0:48:02.09,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And finally Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.09,0:48:03.60,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.60,0:48:08.22,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So for this set, the card arts have this night sky theming.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.22,0:48:09.88,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}They're wearing mostly black,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.88,0:48:13.92,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}and in this card, you can really see the outfit's outline more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.92,0:48:17.38,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And I'm really glad to see the green under the outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.38,0:48:20.81,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}MMJ's color. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.81,0:48:22.40,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.40,0:48:23.46,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.46,0:48:27.26,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Alright, so that was all the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.26,0:48:32.45,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}We also have a comment about the outfits from the \Ncard illustration production team we'd like to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.45,0:48:37.29,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}"In this story, MMJ had to work together with the other idol groups to face a new challenge in an unfamiliar environment."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.29,0:48:41.64,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}The story revolves around Haruka taking active role\Nfor the sake of her team's success.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.64,0:48:45.24,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Drawing inspiration from the joint live from the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.24,0:48:46.53,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}and laser-focusing on our design,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.53,0:48:51.03,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}we aimed to portray a striking MMJ against a midnight sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.03,0:48:53.77,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}To achieve this, we chose a black fabric as the base,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.77,0:48:57.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,adorned with star-shaped accessories for a simple yet eye-catching design.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.82,0:49:02.55,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The design comes together for a "starry night" theme while remaining distinct from those of Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.55,0:49:06.88,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Since the outfit is composed of 80-90% black fabric,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.88,0:49:13.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,to avoid looking tacky, we used velvet and satin textures to create a high-end luster.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.38,0:49:20.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And with lots of detailed accents, we wanted to give MMJ a new, more grown-up impression with these outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.86,0:49:24.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. You know what velvet is?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.28,0:49:27.18,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's what those really nice-feeling carpets are made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.18,0:49:29.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The ones that you feel like want to keep touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.82,0:49:33.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Using that kind of stuff to make idol outfits is...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.28,0:49:35.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Velvet's pretty common in winter-style clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.99,0:49:39.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It works especially well around now like in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.32,0:49:42.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it's looks really lustrous and high quality when it catches the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.70,0:49:43.88,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Same with satin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.88,0:49:49.37,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Satin gives off more of a really nice, bright sparkle when the light hits it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.37,0:49:52.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but velvet has this surprising sense of weight and depth to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.26,0:49:56.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It has this really nice way of taking in the light and reflecting it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.70,0:50:01.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But wait, isn't it amazing how they're able to portray specific fabrics through just the art?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.26,0:50:02.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.85,0:50:07.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This right here is where the attention to detail in MMJ outfits really stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.57,0:50:11.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh whoops, we're a bit over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.96,0:50:14.90,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Are we good to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.90,0:50:18.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Aaaaahhhh I'm gonna cry~
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.08,0:50:20.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's time to watch the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.79,0:50:23.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.21,0:50:26.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,even if you've just listened to the song, seriously, watch the 3DMV too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.21,0:50:27.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.30,0:50:30.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess we're watching it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.14,0:50:36.31,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So moving on, let's watch the 3DMV created for this event's song thanks to the work of Karasuya Sabou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.31,0:50:38.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and then take some time to talk about the song itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.82,0:50:40.83,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So without further ado, onto the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.83,0:50:41.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Comment: 0,0:44:31.93,0:44:37.67,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--BEGIN CARD TALK--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.33,0:52:20.28,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.48,0:52:24.27,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}That was Polar Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.93,0:52:28.47,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.47,0:52:30.36,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}I love everything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.36,0:52:33.93,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}Eh, ah, umm, yeah right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.30,0:52:38.94,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}Right here, their expressions each change one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.94,0:52:42.84,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}And this is from the side of the stage, fans normally can't see them from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.84,0:52:46.00,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}But RIGHT HERE THE SHOT FROM BEHIND INTO THAT LOOK
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.00,0:52:48.15,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.15,0:52:49.30,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.30,0:52:53.38,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}This is what everyone's talking about, right? That part right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.38,0:52:54.64,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,187)}So that's what you all mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.64,0:52:56.44,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.44,0:52:59.21,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh way too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.21,0:53:04.84,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I mean come on. The quality of the MVs nowadays is just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.84,0:53:07.70,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Right? They've come so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.70,0:53:09.06,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Look look, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.06,0:53:10.56,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Hold up— right here—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.56,0:53:11.52,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.38,0:53:15.75,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,They look so good in sync like this—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.75,0:53:16.67,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,yeah this part!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.58,0:53:21.38,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,THIS PART TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.38,0:53:26.58,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, the night sky scenery, so pretty. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.58,0:53:30.70,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The— ah! Look at the shooting stars! So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.70,0:53:32.55,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,And wait for it— this part!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.55,0:53:33.95,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.95,0:53:35.24,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.24,0:53:36.22,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.22,0:53:39.22,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,And then they change formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.22,0:53:39.96,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.96,0:53:42.42,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Now each of them looks up, it's like the steps—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.42,0:53:44.57,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Then here—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.57,0:53:46.46,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Look, look, it's really subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.46,0:53:48.18,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.18,0:53:49.16,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,And then they all as one—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.16,0:53:50.36,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.36,0:53:53.90,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.90,0:53:56.94,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,This part was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.94,0:54:00.20,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The first time I watched the video, I was like "What's that up there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.27,0:54:06.29,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Back when the 3DMVs were just the on-stage dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.29,0:54:09.85,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,they did a great job of showing what the whole performance might have looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.85,0:54:13.29,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I definitely loved those back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.29,0:54:17.10,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,but the recent ones are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.10,0:54:20.66,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're like whole music videos now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.66,0:54:24.17,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,They tell more of a whole story around the song and lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.17,0:54:28.00,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,And that helps you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.00,0:54:30.69,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The lighting was incredible in this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.69,0:54:34.20,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,We saw the same thing in the card arts too,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.20,0:54:36.41,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,but the illumination from the shooting stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.41,0:54:39.13,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,plus that thing shining from behind? The halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.13,0:54:40.18,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,What exactly was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.18,0:54:42.32,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,It looked amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.32,0:54:45.24,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The whole thing was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.24,0:54:48.22,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I'm just so hopeless.  I could just watch this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.69,0:54:53.08,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Next time you watch this,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.08,0:54:55.75,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,make sure to watch out for Airi blowing you a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.75,0:54:58.20,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,and Haruka's wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.20,0:55:00.37,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Anyone oshi-ing them, do check those out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.25,0:55:03.34,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.34,0:55:08.04,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The MV makes— the outfits look great in the MV as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.04,0:55:11.38,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm done. Watched too many times. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.73,0:55:15.91,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Right, we should move onto talking about the song itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.59,0:55:20.84,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,So speaking of "Polar Star",
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.84,0:55:24.59,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Haruka’s evets have definitely had a streak of "cool" songs lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.59,0:55:32.25,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,So I excited to see what kind of song we'd see this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.25,0:55:37.43,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Looking at the last two songs, I realized that "cool" can come in many varieties,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.43,0:55:40.43,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,so I thought, there's a lot more to explore within the range of "cool".
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.43,0:55:44.71,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,And so I saw this song as representing "cool through beauty".
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.71,0:55:47.88,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,It was this very refined coolness that felt really fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.88,0:55:51.72,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,It blew me away the first time I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.72,0:55:53.74,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Especially since—
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.74,0:55:59.02,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,'Haruka's previous songs have very beautiful harmonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.02,0:56:00.87,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,That's one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.87,0:56:05.60,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,But those parts everyone comes in one by one, layering harmonies on top of each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.60,0:56:09.67,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,All the small steps MMJ are taking in recent events,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.67,0:56:12.66,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,leading them to success and seeing real results;
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.66,0:56:17.72,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I think this song captures all of that really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.72,0:56:21.85,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The harmonies throughout the song are also so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.85,0:56:26.06,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,They layered together so many different vocal lines to create those.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.06,0:56:30.13,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Both in the parts where they sing individually, and going into each chorus, 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.13,0:56:34.97,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Try going back and listen closely to all those different vocal layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.97,0:56:40.00,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,As for recording, what I tried to keep in mind most during recording...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.00,0:56:42.41,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,well first of all, was trying not to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.41,0:56:45.51,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Trying to keep composed during those parts—
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.51,0:56:48.26,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,We're idols, so our job is to deliver hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.26,0:56:50.66,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,So we ourselves mustn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.66,0:56:53.60,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,But this is a song reminiscing on all that they've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.60,0:57:00.92,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,as well as reaffirming their drive to keep pushing forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.92,0:57:04.80,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,So there's a balance being struck between this cool, noble feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.80,0:57:07.95,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,while at the same time portraying an emotional nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.95,0:57:10.60,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,That's what makes this song so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.60,0:57:13.93,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,That's what I wrote. Here in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.93,0:57:17.06,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Alright, and also,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.06,0:57:20.39,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,there's also going to be a 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.39,0:57:21.08,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Says here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.08,0:57:23.98,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,So it'll probably also be a full version.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.98,0:57:30.16,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,That'll include parts that you don't see here in the 3DMV,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.16,0:57:34.51,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,So try listening to both and seeing what's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.51,0:57:40.92,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Specifically, the singing in last chorus might give you a bit of a different impression from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.92,0:57:42.64,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,So please do try listening to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.64,0:57:45.56,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,On a personal note,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.56,0:57:52.70,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I, Mayu Yoshioka, have actually written lyrics for a song themed around the North Star before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.70,0:57:57.06,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,"Polar Star" meaning the same thing as the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.06,0:58:02.52,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,But "idols" and "stars", especially the North Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.52,0:58:05.04,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,have this natural connection to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.04,0:58:08.27,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,When I was writing those lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.27,0:58:13.02,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I thought of it taking the meaning of a landmark, as a guiding light for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.02,0:58:17.90,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,You know, North Star, the brightest one in the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.90,0:58:22.24,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,And using its meaning as guiding light,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.24,0:58:28.43,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,that represents this feeling of "just watch me" or "find me" really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.43,0:58:29.38,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,That's the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.38,0:58:31.58,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,And that—
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.58,0:58:37.58,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,For MMJ's story, especially in this Lumina Grand Prix arc,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.58,0:58:41.30,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,That really resonates with finding the image of what an idol should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.30,0:58:46.70,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I thought, "Yeah, that's part of their story". Think I mentioned this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.70,0:58:53.55,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,It's part of an idol's storytelling. That story an idol creates together with their fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.55,0:58:56.58,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,that guiding light is a huge part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.58,0:58:59.12,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The lyricist definitely—
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.12,0:59:00.78,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,you feel the same thing from the lyrics—
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.02,0:59:07.91,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.91,0:59:14.08,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Sorry for ranting on about a personal experience like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.30,0:59:24.16,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I trusted in my feelings back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.08,0:59:20.30,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,but knowing "ah, I wasn't alone in those feelings", it felt really validating.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.16,0:59:32.31,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,My feelings towards idols, the way I think about them, and of course everything that Haruka has taught be about me about being an idol—
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.31,0:59:34.22,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,knowing I wasn't wrong in any of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.22,0:59:37.62,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,and where MMJ goes from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.62,0:59:43.50,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,Being able to reaffirm that all to myself all my thoughts on what it means to be an idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.50,0:59:45.49,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I think this song really helped me to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.49,0:59:52.74,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful we had such wonderful lyrics written for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.74,0:59:57.70,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,The "stars" theming has been mostly Leo/need up to this point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.70,1:00:00.86,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,For ProSeka, they're kind of the owners of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.86,1:00:05.38,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,I think the other users have all been kind of avoiding the overlap in theme.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.38,1:00:10.85,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,But this time
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.85,1:00:13.85,Haruka - Top,,0,0,0,,
